At least 6 people have been killed in a crash in the Msunduzi area in KZN. JOHANNESBURG - At least six people have been killed in a crash in Cato Ridge between Durban and Pietermaritzburg. A truck lost control and collided into two other vehicles and pedestrians in KwaXimba outside Cato Ridge. READ: Nine killed, 27 injured in Limpopo car crash An estimated 20 people have also been injured in the crash.